Sentencas: By plasma spraying and subsequent heat/reduction treatment (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.9)MnO3-delta and Ni protection coatings for Cr-based interconnect were prepared.
Titulo: Protection coatings for planar solid oxide fuel cell interconnect prepared by plasma spraying

Sentencas: The appropriate processing parameters for plasma spraying were determined.
Titulo: Protection coatings for planar solid oxide fuel cell interconnect prepared by plasma spraying

Sentencas: The phase transition and conductivity of (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.9)MnO3-delta coating were studied by XRD and standard DC four-point method.
Titulo: Protection coatings for planar solid oxide fuel cell interconnect prepared by plasma spraying

Sentencas: The morphology of (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.9)MnO3-delta and Ni coatings was characterized by SEM.
Titulo: Protection coatings for planar solid oxide fuel cell interconnect prepared by plasma spraying

Sentencas: The results show that (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.9)MnO3-delta and Ni coatings adhered well to the interconnect and were effective in protecting the interconnect from oxidation and corrosion.
Titulo: Protection coatings for planar solid oxide fuel cell interconnect prepared by plasma spraying
